subject: Potential Collaboration Opportunity
body:
Dear DoorDash Team,

I hope this message finds you well. I am currently pursuing a Bachelor of Business Administration and a Bachelor of Math, and I have a strong background in analyzing and resolving infrastructure issues, as demonstrated during my time at OnX. Additionally, I have successfully managed a stock portfolio that grew from $400 to $8,000 over four years, showcasing my analytical skills and strategic thinking.

I am particularly interested in exploring opportunities to contribute to DoorDash's growth and innovation. I believe my experience in both technical problem-solving and financial analysis could add value to your team.

Thank you for considering my outreach. I look forward to the possibility of discussing how I can contribute to DoorDash.

Best regards,

[Your Name]
[Your Contact Information]

subject: Potential Collaboration on Data-Driven Insights
body:
Dear Airbnb Team,

I hope this message finds you well. My name is [Your Name], and I am currently pursuing a Bachelor of Business Administration and a Bachelor of Math. I have a strong background in data analysis and problem-solving, demonstrated through my experience diagnosing and resolving infrastructure issues at OnX.

Additionally, I successfully grew my stock portfolio from $400 to $8,000 over four years, showcasing my ability to analyze market trends and make data-driven decisions. I believe these skills could contribute to enhancing Airbnb's data analytics initiatives and optimizing user experiences.

I would love the opportunity to discuss how my background aligns with Airbnb's goals. Thank you for your time.

Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Contact Information]
